import styled from 'styled-components';
import { Container, Grid, Paper, Card } from '@material-ui/core';

const Coding = () => {
    return (
        <Container fixed>
            <Grid container>
                <Grid item xs={12} fullWidth>
                    <Title>Coding expirience</Title>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={4} fullWidth>
                    <Card>
                        <CardMedia
                            className={classes.media}
                            image='../public/teknikfokus.jpg'
                            title='Contemplative Reptile'
                        />
                        <CardContent>
                            <Typography
                                gutterBottom
                                variant='h5'
                                component='h2'
                            >
                                Lizard
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography
                                variant='body2'
                                color='textSecondary'
                                component='p'
                            >
                                Lizards are a widespread group of squamate
                                reptiles, with over 6,000 species, ranging
                                across all continents except Antarctica
                            </Typography>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={4} fullWidth>
                    <Paper>2</Paper>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={4} fullWidth>
                    <Paper>3</Paper>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Container>
    );
};

export default Coding;

const Title = styled.p`
    margin-top: 0rem;
    color: white;
    font-size: 4rem;
`;
